{"type":"message","id":"37501f74","parentId":"85c4c0eb","timestamp":"2026-02-15T17:55:21.375Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-02-15 19:55 GMT+2] OPERATION: CORE MIGRATION & TERMINAL WATCHDOG.\n\n1.  **Deep Navigation (Grep):**\n    *   *Search:* `grep -r \"https://api.dmarket.com\" .` and `grep -r \"logs/\" .`\n    *   *Goal:* Identify hardcoded strings to replace with `ConfigManager`.\n\n2.  **Core Refactor (`ConfigManager`):**\n    *   *Create:* `src/core/config_manager.py` (Singleton).\n    *   *Feature:* Load `openclaw.json` + `.env`. Validate via `jsonschema`.\n    *   *Migration:* Update `src/dmarket/api/client.py`, `src/trading_bot.py`, `src/agent_wrapper.py` to use `ConfigManager.get(\"api_url\")`.\n\n3.  **Live Debug Loop (The Watchdog):**\n    *   *Run:* `python src/trading_bot.py --test` (CS2).\n    *   *Observe:* `ImportError` / `AttributeError`.\n    *   *Fix:* Edit file -> Retry.\n    *   *Repeat:* Until exit code 0.\n\n4.  **DNA Sync:**\n    *   Update `docs/ACTIVE_CONTEXT.json`: Add `\"config_status\": \"centralized\"`.\n\n5.  **Git Commit:**\n    *   `git add .`\n    *   `git commit -m \"Refactor: Centralized Config & Terminal Watchdog Proof\"`\n\n6.  **Output:**\n    *   Files modified list.\n    *   Watchdog Intervention Log (Errors found & fixed).\n    *   Final Commit Hash."}],"timestamp":1771178121373}}
