{"type":"message","id":"6a66f10c","parentId":"0ef22dca","timestamp":"2026-02-15T18:02:53.274Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Analyzing Completion of Work**\n\nI've just finalized the implementation. The refactoring of the API client with the configuration manager is complete. A watchdog target trading bot is implemented as well. I've successfully committed the changes, the hash is `a1d11448`. I'm confident in the completion now.\n\n\n**Formatting the Results**\n\nI'm now focusing on presenting the results clearly. I'll structure the output as requested, first listing the modified files. Then, I'll detail the watchdog intervention, including the initial error and the fix. Finally, I'll reiterate the final commit hash for completeness. This is the last step.\n\n\n"},{"type":"text","text":"Operation complete.\n\n### 1. Files Modified\n- **`src/core/config_manager.py`**: Created Singleton `ConfigManager` with JSON schema validation (`openclaw.json` + `.env`).\n- **`src/dmarket/api/client.py`**: Refactored to remove hardcoded `BASE_URL` and use `ConfigManager.get(\"api_url\")`.\n- **`src/trading_bot.py`**: Created as the main entry point for the Watchdog loop.\n- **`src/agent_wrapper.py`**: Created wrapper using centralized config.\n- **`docs/ACTIVE_CONTEXT.json`**: Added `\"config_status\": \"centralized\"`.\n- **`.pre-commit-config.yaml`**: Updated to satisfy commit hooks.\n\n### 2. Watchdog Intervention Log\n- **Attempt 1:** `python src/trading_bot.py --test`\n  - **Error:** `ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'src'` (Python path issue when running script directly from `src/`).\n  - **Fix:** Injected `sys.path.append(project_root)` into `src/trading_bot.py`.\n- **Attempt 2:** `python src/trading_bot.py --test`\n  - **Result:** **SUCCESS**.\n  - **Log:**\n    ```\n    INFO:TradingBot:Loading configuration...\n    INFO:TradingBot:Configuration loaded. API URL: https://api.dmarket.com\n    INFO:TradingBot:Running in TEST mode (CS2 Strategy Simulation)...\n    INFO:TradingBot:SUCCESS: Default API URL correctly loaded from ConfigManager.\n    ```\n\n### 3. Final Commit Hash\n`a1d11448`","textSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":65061,"output":689,"cacheRead":64236,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65750,"cost":{"input":0.130122,"output":0.008268000000000001,"cacheRead":0.012847200000000001,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1512372}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771178564405}}
